{"title": "Balík z ulice", "content": "<p></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZQub-703ViafumawSV9C5G2VOPEgW0_P4A1Ebh3fLdhJlJGqbul_5hWzBGmxthoFCBb9t7EkUDEZeVVFRBJdYdNRUW9jaBqlgXKA1kOhlnPuX2YgCCVcne4iKv-Yhf_H6DY_Aoq2tuf317Wtcmt-f52JaFO3BDfKoxMeloXqLGZw5C7xTVXGm5qpYTX8/s4608/0312d42a3f_101438510_o2.jpg\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"3456\" data-original-width=\"4608\" height=\"314\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZQub-703ViafumawSV9C5G2VOPEgW0_P4A1Ebh3fLdhJlJGqbul_5hWzBGmxthoFCBb9t7EkUDEZeVVFRBJdYdNRUW9jaBqlgXKA1kOhlnPuX2YgCCVcne4iKv-Yhf_H6DY_Aoq2tuf317Wtcmt-f52JaFO3BDfKoxMeloXqLGZw5C7xTVXGm5qpYTX8/w419-h314/0312d42a3f_101438510_o2.jpg\" width=\"419\" /></a></div><br />&nbsp;Pamatujte, nikdy není pozdě se zaprodat vysokému žití!<p></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><br /></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><object class=\"BLOG_video_class\" contentid=\"9e6f33bc17d24914\" height=\"419\" id=\"BLOG_video-9e6f33bc17d24914\" width=\"505\"></object></div><br /><p><br /></p><p>Zde se odehrávala Rusalka... je to jakási zapadlá kaplička na pozoruhodném hřbitově.</p><p><br /></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/drive-storage/AJQWtBPYWrytMvIw15TGqVG2iqLM6KQfP3qLQsP5vh4fVhOxtQJoI7bqH-Uco8vylLc1DCmkMZe38B6imKFW4i9et00Kzjk7NqPptuUNKko4tSFI1g=s400\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"400\" data-original-width=\"300\" height=\"478\" src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/drive-storage/AJQWtBPYWrytMvIw15TGqVG2iqLM6KQfP3qLQsP5vh4fVhOxtQJoI7bqH-Uco8vylLc1DCmkMZe38B6imKFW4i9et00Kzjk7NqPptuUNKko4tSFI1g=w359-h478\" width=\"359\" /></a></div><br /><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Zde Kafka úspěšně snil svůj stoletý sen. V podání Němců z jakéhosi institutu.</p><p><br /></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><object class=\"BLOG_video_class\" contentid=\"8e63ff8c3c468eb0\" height=\"369\" id=\"BLOG_video-8e63ff8c3c468eb0\" width=\"444\"></object></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><br /></div><br /><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Tady zpívali Tři Tenoři. Nebo vlastně čtyři. Půl barytoni atd.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>", "published": "2024-06-16T19:44:00Z", "tags": ["ich bin sie"], "filename": "/2024/06/balik-z-ulice.html"}